ActCanadian Institutes of Health Research Act
PrecisApproval of the authorization by the Governing Council of the Canadian Institutes of Health Research of TAMMY J. CLIFFORD of Ottawa, Ontario, to act as President of the Canadian Institutes of Health Research, to hold office during pleasure for a term of one year, or until such time as a new President is appointed, whichever occurs first.
